This module can be used to build, handle, process and search
`tries <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trie>`_

Interpreter
===========

The package has been developed and tested with Python 2.7, 3.5, 3.6 and 3.7
under Linux (Debian, Ubuntu), Apple macOS and Microsoft Windows

Installing
==========

.. code-block:: bash

	$ pip install ptrie

